release.changelog:
Hello to the Neptune Browser!

From now on, we are moving beyond being just a simple browser. Neptune Browser is being renewed step by step to provide a better experience. With this update, support for Android 15 Beta has been provided. Additionally, by updating the ad blocker exclusive to Plus users, we have transitioned to the Ultimate Adblocker filters. Lastly, we have added a notification for Incognito mode users to close tabs with a single tap.
